<h1>Statetopia</h1>

<h2>The Year is 2019 and the USA Republic has collapsed. The former country is now a series of fractured nation-states. You are running one. Play the game and try to survive the Trumpocalpyse</h2>

<% if current_user %>
  <%= link_to "Start Your Nation", new_nation_path %>
  <% if current_user.nations.any? %>
    <h3>Continue Playing</h3>
    <% current_user.nations.each do |nation| %>
      <%= link_to nation.name, nation_path(nation) %>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>
<% else %>
  <%= link_to "Sign Up to Play", new_user_registration_path %>
<% end %>
